{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Uh, if I was asked to-- to clean the toilet, I clean the toilet, which was sometimes-- that doesn't mean I was submittive-- submissive, but I said to myself, I going to get my own somewhere else, sometime, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Which will-- I will tell you later on what we did in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If this is supposed to be, uh, uh, sabotage of some sort, well, let's say it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, uh, uh, I wasn't-- I didn't act like a big shot, and I was very stubborn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I still am.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I have a short temper, and I still have.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Uh, but I tried to control it, and I think that this control, without knowing it, helped me a lot to go through many, many, many things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to be invisible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I know this is very ambiguous, that word, but-- but it can be done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, the p-- though I think at the most important factor about being invisible is to be lucky.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- you know people usually make certain moves and they say, ah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It is.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the most-- I think the most important factor of all these things is luck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's the-- the-- the-- the throw of a dice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's, uh, it's-- it's what's going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, if you-- if you're resigned that-- uh, and this is my biggest beef when I talk about the religious part of what happened, and they say my beliefs is that people simply write it off by saying it is written.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bullshit.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It isn't written.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing's written.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I resent that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you're lucky, something you can't help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing is written.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
